# Optional local OpenAI-compatible API credentials (copy to `api.md` in this folder).
#
# Precedence for OPENAI_API_KEY (first hit wins):
#   1. ~/Downloads/OpenAI-API.md  (personal — beats shell env so stale `export OPENAI_API_KEY` in ~/.zshrc does not override)
#   2. This file as `api.md` (gitignored)
#   3. Environment variables
#
# OPENAI_BASE_URL is taken from the same row as the winning key when set; otherwise filled from the same fallback chain.
#
# Do not commit real keys.

OPENAI_API_KEY=
OPENAI_BASE_URL=https://api.apiyi.com/v1
